trans-unit.source: Contains methods, properties, and events to support navigation.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller metoder, egenskaper och händelser som stöd för navigering.

trans-unit.source: NavigationService encapsulates the ability to download content within the context of a browser-style navigation.
trans-unit.target: NavigationService kapslar in möjlighet att hämta innehåll inom ramen för navigering webbläsare-format.

trans-unit.source: Content can be any type of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] object and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] files.
trans-unit.target: Innehållet kan vara alla slags [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] objekt och [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] filer.

trans-unit.source: In general, however, pages are the preferred as the way to package content for navigation (see <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>).
trans-unit.target: I allmänhet sidor är dock bäst sätt att paketinnehåll för navigering (se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>

trans-unit.source: The lifetime of a navigation can be tracked through the following events: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationProgress> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: Livslängden för navigering kan spåras via följande händelser:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationProgress>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.FragmentNavigation> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationProgress> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>

trans-unit.source: Not all events are raised each time that a navigation occurs; the set of events that are raised is determined by the type of navigation that occurs (content or content fragment) and how the navigation completes (canceled, stopped, or failed).
trans-unit.target: Inte alla händelser aktiveras varje gång en navigation inträffar; uppsättningen av händelser som är bestäms av typ av navigering som uppstår (innehåll eller innehåll fragment) och hur navigeringen har slutförts (avbrutits, stoppas eller misslyckades).

trans-unit.source: The following figure illustrates the sequence in which these events are raised: ![Page navigation flow chart](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "Page navigation flow chart") During or after a navigation, NavigationService provides information about the content that is being navigated to, including the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A>), the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the current content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CurrentSource%2A>), and an object that contains the content that was navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Följande bild illustrerar sekvensen händelserna aktiveras: ![sidan navigering flödesschema](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "sidan navigering flödesschema") under eller efter en navigering NavigationService innehåller information om det innehåll som navigeras till, inklusive den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] av innehåll som har navigerat till (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A>), [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för det aktuella innehållet (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CurrentSource%2A>), och ett objekt som innehåller det innehåll som har navigerat till (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CurrentSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: When content is navigated to, NavigationService records the navigation as an entry in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: När innehållet har navigerat till registrerar NavigationService navigering som en post i historik.

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to back navigation history when either a new navigation occurs, by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> method, or by navigating to an entry in forward navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En post har lagts till i tillbaka historik när en ny navigering inträffar genom att anropa den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>metoden, eller genom att gå till en post i historiken för navigering framåt, genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to forward navigation history by navigating to an entry in back navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En post har lagts till i historiken för navigering framåt genom att gå till en post i tillbaka historik, genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoBack%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoForward%2A> report whether there are entries in back and forward navigation history, respectively.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoBack%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoForward%2A>rapportera om det finns poster i tillbaka och navigering framåt historik respektive.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoForward%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.CanGoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Also, the most recent entry in back navigation history can be removed by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den senaste posten i tillbaka Historik kan också tas bort genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: By default, NavigationService does not store an instance of a content object in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Som standard lagrar NavigationService inte en instans av ett innehållsobjekt i historik.

trans-unit.source: Instead, NavigationService creates a new instance of the content object each time it is navigated to by using navigation history.
trans-unit.target: I stället skapar NavigationService en ny instans av innehållsobjektet varje gång den navigeras till med hjälp av historik.

trans-unit.source: This behavior is designed to avoid excessive memory consumption when large numbers and large pieces of content are being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Det här beteendet är utformat för att undvika överdriven minnesförbrukning när stora tal och stora delar av innehåll som du navigerar till.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the state of the content is not remembered from one navigation to the next.
trans-unit.target: Därför sparas inte tillståndet för innehållet från en navigering till nästa.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] provides several techniques by which you can store a piece of state for a piece of content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Dock [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] innehåller flera metoder som du kan lagra en typ av tillstånd för en del av innehåll i historik.

trans-unit.source: Using <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, you can also remember multiple sets of state for a single page instance.
trans-unit.target: Med hjälp av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, du kan också komma ihåg flera uppsättningar av tillståndet för en enstaka sida-instans.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationService is `sealed` class and, therefore, cannot be instantiated; instead, NavigationService is used by navigators to enable navigation.
trans-unit.target: NavigationService är `sealed` klassen och därför kan inte skapas, i stället NavigationService används av tidsnavigatörer för att aktivera navigering.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], there are two navigators: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], det finns två tidsnavigatörer: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Visually, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] use [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] as a navigator, to provide an integrated user experience.
trans-unit.target: Visuellt, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] använder [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] som en navigator att ge en integrerad användarupplevelse.

trans-unit.source: Physically, however, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] actually use <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> as the navigator; the <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A> property of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] running in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] will return a reference to the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, and the navigation history that is managed by the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> is integrated with the navigation history that is managed by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] in the following ways: - When content is navigated to by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A> from within an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] the relevant navigation history entries are also added to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Fysiskt, men [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] faktiskt använder <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>som Navigatören; den <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>egenskapen för ett [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] körs i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] returnerar en referens till den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, och den historik som hanteras av den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>är integrerad med den historik som hanteras av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] på följande sätt: – när innehållet har navigerat till genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>, och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A>inifrån en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] historikposter relevanta navigering läggs också till [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] historik.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Since navigations are asynchronous, it is possible for multiple navigations to be in progress at the same time.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom navigering är asynkron, är det möjligt för flera navigering för bearbetning på samma gång.

trans-unit.source: For example, if there are two child frames on a single page, both frames could be navigating.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel om det finns två underordnade ramar på en enstaka sida, kunde både ramar navigering.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the various navigation events that are raised by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> may be raised multiple times, one for each piece of content that is being navigated to, and not necessarily in order that the navigations were requested.
trans-unit.target: I det här fallet är de olika navigering händelser som utlöses av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>kan vara upphöjt flera gånger, en för varje typ av innehåll som navigeras till och inte nödvändigtvis att navigering begärdes.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: Consequently, if a particular navigation request needs to process data that is specific to the individual request, it cannot use data that is available to all navigation requests.
trans-unit.target: Om en viss navigering begäran måste bearbeta data som är specifika för enskilda begäran, använda den därför inte data som är tillgängliga för alla begäranden som navigering.

trans-unit.source: Instead, you can use `navigationState` to pass data for navigation processing that is specific to one navigation request.
trans-unit.target: Använd i stället `navigationState` att skicka data för navigering bearbetning som är specifika för en navigering begäran.

trans-unit.source: The following event arguments provide access to navigation state: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> (passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> event).

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> (passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted> event handlers).
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>(skickades till den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted>händelsehanterare).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.target: Navigera asynkront till källinnehållet på en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)], skicka ett objekt som innehåller navigering tillstånd för bearbetning under navigering och begränsat innehåll.

trans-unit.source: This method is only for standalone applications and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] content.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden är endast för fristående program och [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] innehåll.

trans-unit.source: This method exhibits the same behavior as <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, and extends it by ensuring that the content that is being downloaded is placed into a partial trust security sandbox (with the default Internet zone set of permissions - see [WPF Partial Trust Security](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden fungerar likadant som <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, och utökar genom att säkerställa att det innehåll som hämtas placeras i ett partiellt förtroende säkerhet sandbox (med en standard Internet zonen uppsättning behörigheter - Se [WPF partiellt förtroende säkerhet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> object initialized with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the desired content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Uri>objektet initieras med de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för önskat innehåll.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: An object that contains data to be used for processing during navigation.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som innehåller data som ska användas för bearbetning under navigering.

trans-unit.source: Download content into a partial trust security sandbox (with the default Internet zone set of permissions, if <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämta innehåll i ett partiellt förtroende säkerhet sandbox (med Internet zonen uppsättning behörigheter, om <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if a navigation is not canceled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om en navigering inte avbryts; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the content that is being navigated to has been found, and is available from the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content*> property, although it may not have completed loading.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar när innehållet navigeras till har hittats och är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content*>egenskap, även om den har inte slutfört inläsningen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content*>

trans-unit.source: You handle Navigated if you need to discover pertinent information regarding the navigation request when downloading commences.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hantera Navigated om du behöver identifiera viktig information för navigering begäran när hämtar påbörjas.

trans-unit.source: This information is available from the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs> object that is passed to the Navigated event handler, and includes: - The source page.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs>objekt som har överförts till händelsehanteraren Navigated och omfattar:-sidan källa.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: When Navigated is raised, at least part of the source page's [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] tree has been parsed, and attached to target content control.
trans-unit.target: När Navigated utlöses åtminstone en del av sidan källa [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] trädet har parsas och bifogas till innehåll målkontrollen.

trans-unit.source: - The requested [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: -Den begärda [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: - The navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: - Additional data, if the navigation was initiated by calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -Ytterligare data, om navigeringen har startats genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Response details (using a <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object).
trans-unit.target: / Svar-information (med hjälp av en <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>objekt).</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: Navigated is not raised when the source page could not be found or loaded, in which case <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> is raised.
trans-unit.target: Navigerat utlöses inte när sidan källa inte kunde hittas eller har lästs in, i vilket fall <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>utlöses.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> raises <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>, it also raises <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> event on the <xref:System.Windows.Application> object.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > När <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>genererar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>, den också genererar <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen på den <xref:System.Windows.Application>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Application> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when a new navigation is requested.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar när en ny navigering begärs.

trans-unit.source: Navigating is raised when a new navigation is requested, but before the source content is requested, including when: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Navigera inträffar när en ny navigering krävs men innan källan innehållet begärs, inklusive när:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>kallas.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A> is called (or an entry is selected from a navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A>kallas (eller en post har markerats navigering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A content fragment is navigated to.
trans-unit.target: -En innehåll fragment navigerat till.

trans-unit.source: You handle Navigating if you need to discover pertinent information regarding the navigation request before navigation starts.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hantera navigering om du behöver identifiera viktig information för navigering begäran innan navigering startar.

trans-unit.source: This information is available from the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> object that is passed to the Navigating event handler.
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>objekt som har överförts till Navigating-händelsehanterare.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> object for the navigation is created and available from the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> parameter; because the actual request hasn't been made at this point, you can reconfigure the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> object, if necessary.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>objekt för navigeringen har skapats och är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>parameter; eftersom den faktiska begäranden inte har gjorts nu, kan du konfigurera om den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>objekt, om det behövs.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: You also handle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> to cancel navigation, if required, by setting <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> to true.
trans-unit.target: Du hanterar även <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>att avbryta navigering, vid behov genom att ange <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>till true.</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: If you cancel navigation, no other navigation events are raised.
trans-unit.target: Om du avbryter navigering aktiveras inga andra händelser i navigeringsfönstret.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If your application is hosted in the browser, you cannot prevent the user from navigating away from your application by canceling the Navigating event.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Om ditt program finns i webbläsaren, kan du förhindra att användaren navigerar bort från ditt program genom att avbryta Navigating-händelsen.

trans-unit.source: After the first piece of content is navigated to by a navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>), each piece of content that is navigated away from is added to navigation history.
trans-unit.target: När den första delen av innehåll navigerat till av en navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>), varje typ av innehåll som navigerar bort från läggs till historik.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: If you need to save state information about the content you are navigating away from, you can add the state to the journal entry for that content by setting <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A> with a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object.
trans-unit.target: Om du behöver spara statusinformation om det innehåll du navigerar bort från du kan lägga till tillståndet journalpost för innehållet genom att ange <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>med en <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> raises Navigating, it also raises <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> event on the <xref:System.Windows.Application> object.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > När <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>genererar navigering, den också genererar <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen på den <xref:System.Windows.Application>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Application> </xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an error occurs while navigating to the requested content.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar när ett fel inträffar vid navigering till det begärda innehållet.

trans-unit.source: When either a <xref:System.Net.WebException> or an <xref:System.IO.IOException> is thrown during a navigation, the NavigationFailed event is raised.
trans-unit.target: När antingen en <xref:System.Net.WebException>eller en <xref:System.IO.IOException>genereras under navigering NavigationFailed händelsen utlöses.</xref:System.IO.IOException> </xref:System.Net.WebException>

trans-unit.source: NavigationFailed is passed a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs> that encapsulates information about both the exception and the details of the navigation that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: NavigationFailed skickas en <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs>som kapslar in information om både undantaget och information om navigering som orsakade undantaget.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: When an exception results from a failed navigation, and is unhandled, the following events are raised in the order listed: - NavigationFailed.
trans-unit.target: När ett undantag resultat av en misslyckad navigering och inte hanteras, aktiveras följande händelser i angiven ordning:-NavigationFailed.

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Application.DispatcherUnhandledException>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Application.DispatcherUnhandledException>.</xref:System.Windows.Application.DispatcherUnhandledException>

trans-unit.source: If a navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) is hosted by one or more navigators, `NavigationFailed` is not raised on any of them.
trans-unit.target: Om en navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) finns på en eller flera tidsnavigatörer `NavigationFailed` aktiveras inte på någon av dem.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Occurs periodically during a download to provide navigation progress information.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar regelbundet under en hämtning att ge information om förloppet.

trans-unit.source: NavigationProgress is passed a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs> which exposes the following progress information: - Number of bytes downloaded so far (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A>).
trans-unit.target: NavigationProgress skickas en <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs>som visar följande statusinformation:-Antal hämtade byte hittills (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - Number of total bytes to download (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A>).
trans-unit.target: -Antal bytes hämta (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationProgress is raised once for every 1024 bytes of content downloaded, and once more if the number of remaining bytes is ever less than 1024 bytes.
trans-unit.target: NavigationProgress utlöses när för varje 1 024 byte av innehåll hämtas och en gång om antalet återstående byte är aldrig mindre än 1 024 byte.

trans-unit.source: For this reason, handling NavigationProgress provides a useful way to track and display the progress of a current download.
trans-unit.target: Därför ger hantering NavigationProgress ett bra sätt att spåra och visa förloppet för en hämtningen.

trans-unit.source: NavigationProgress won't be raised in some cases, such as when the same piece of content is navigated to, or when a content fragment is navigated to on content that is currently loaded (that is, the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A> property).
trans-unit.target: NavigationProgress inte aktiveras i vissa fall, till exempel när samma typ av innehåll navigerat till, eller när ett innehåll fragment navigerat till innehåll som är inlästa (det vill säga värdet för den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A>egenskapen).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A>

trans-unit.source: When navigating to a compiled XAML resource, the final NavigationProgress event may not be raised.
trans-unit.target: När du navigerar till en kompilerad XAML-resursen kan inte sista NavigationProgress händelsen utlöses.

trans-unit.source: This means that at the end of the download, the last reported <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A> value may not equal the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: Det innebär att senaste rapporterat i slutet av hämtningen <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A>värde får inte vara lika med den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A>värde.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.MaxBytes%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationProgressEventArgs.BytesRead%2A>

trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted> event to be notified when the navigation has finished.
trans-unit.target: Hantera den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted>händelse som ska meddelas när navigeringen har slutförts.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.LoadCompleted>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> raises NavigationProgress, it also raises <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationProgress?displayProperty=fullName> event on the <xref:System.Windows.Application> object.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > När <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>genererar NavigationProgress, den också genererar <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationProgress?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen på den <xref:System.Windows.Application>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Application> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationProgress?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: You handle NavigationStopped if you need to discover pertinent information regarding the navigation request when downloading is stopped.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hantera NavigationStopped om du behöver identifiera viktig information för navigering begäran när hämtar har stoppats.

trans-unit.source: This information is available from the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs> object that is passed to the NavigationStopped event handler, and includes: - The requested [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Den här informationen är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs>objekt som har överförts till händelsehanteraren NavigationStopped och omfattar:-den begärda [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - The navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -Navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: - Additional data, if the navigation was initiated by calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: -Ytterligare data, om navigeringen har startats genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > När <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>genererar NavigationStopped, den också genererar <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationStopped?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen på den <xref:System.Windows.Application>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Application> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationStopped?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: Reloads the current content.
trans-unit.target: Läser det aktuella innehållet.

trans-unit.source: If the current content (specified by the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A> property) is navigated to again, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> does not download the content again.
trans-unit.target: Om det aktuella innehållet (anges av värdet för den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A>egenskapen) navigerat till igen, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>inte hämta innehållet igen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: To force <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> to re-navigate to the content, call Refresh.
trans-unit.target: Du kan tvinga <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>anropa för att navigera igen till innehållet, uppdatera.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>

trans-unit.source: Note that if the current content is navigated to again, whether by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> or Refresh, a new entry is not added to navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Observera att om det aktuella innehållet har navigerat till igen, om genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>eller uppdatering, en ny post läggs inte till historik.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Removes the most recent journal entry from back history.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort den senaste journalposten från tillbaka historik.

trans-unit.source: If two or more navigators (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) share the same navigation history, one navigator can use RemoveBackEntry to retrieve the back navigation history entry for a navigation that took place in another navigator.
trans-unit.target: Om två eller flera tidsnavigatörer (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) dela på samma Historik kan en navigator använda RemoveBackEntry för att hämta navigering bakåt jobbhistorikposten för navigering som utfördes i en annan navigator.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: The most recent <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry"></xref> in back navigation history, if there is one.
trans-unit.target: Den senaste <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry"> </xref> i tillbaka historik, om sådan finns.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the current content, or the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of new content that is currently being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för det aktuella innehållet eller [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] av nytt innehåll som för närvarande som navigerat till.

trans-unit.source: If you set this property to a different [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] than the one currently being displayed, the navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) navigates to the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Om du anger egenskapen till en annan [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] än det som visas, Navigatören (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) navigerar till den angivna [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Source is set to the content that is loaded from the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] that is navigated to, unless the navigation is canceled.
trans-unit.target: Källan är inställd för det innehåll som har lästs in från den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] som har navigerat till, såvida inte navigeringen har avbrutits.

trans-unit.source: Source can be set with a fragment-only [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], and can be set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Källan kan anges med ett fragment endast [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], och kan anges till `null`.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> that contains the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the current content, or the content that is currently being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Uri>som innehåller den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för det aktuella innehållet eller innehåll som för närvarande är att efter att.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Stops further downloading of content for the current navigation request.
trans-unit.target: Stoppar ytterligare hämtning av innehåll för den aktuella begäranden i navigeringsfönstret.

trans-unit.source: StopLoading can be called as soon as <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> returns, and stops navigation that is in progress in child frames.
trans-unit.target: StopLoading kan anropas när <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>returnerar och stoppar navigering pågår i underordnade ramar.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Calling the StopLoading method raises the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped> event.
trans-unit.target: Att anropa metoden StopLoading genererar den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationStopped>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > StopLoading must be called on the same thread that initiated the navigation.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > StopLoading måste anropas på samma tråd som initierade navigeringen.
